Insider Activity


Individual




Raju S. K. Chaganti



Dr. Raju S. K. Chaganti is a Director at Cancer Genetics, Inc. and a Professor at Gerstner Sloan Kettering Graduate School of Biomedical Science. He is on the Board of Directors at Cancer Genetics, Inc.
Dr. Chaganti was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by Memorial Sloan-Kettering Cancer Center, a Principal by Cell Biology & Physiology, and a Principal by Sloan-Kettering Institute for Cancer Research.
He received his doctorate degree from Harvard University.



